{"type": "article", "id": 12261, "title": "“世界上最轻的电动自行车”", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-17T11:00:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 67, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606153322vzGBL1893eEaOfpI.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:justify;\">来自英国的 Clive Sinclair 最近推出了一款号称“世界上最轻最小的电动自行车”，它脱胎于原来的 “A” 自行车。它的轮子直径只有 13 厘米，前轮搭载了一个马达，当脚蹬开始运动，马达也会自动开始工作。车身采用的材料是航空级铝材，能够在 10 秒钟内被折叠起来，整个车身重量只有 12 千克。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140041EhRWu3aTSU0tQ9jy.jpg\" width=\"784\" height=\"560\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261400421EqwTdSYkxn6sZGX.jpg\" width=\"784\" height=\"560\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614004330KJY5fwjWDCBdkZ.jpg\" width=\"784\" height=\"560\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140044mgfvPH1yFjdT6Jur.jpg\" width=\"784\" height=\"560\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261400444mWdMF9HvJP1zOUy.jpg\" width=\"784\" height=\"560\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261400457uNs3dSb40zTpKvo.jpg\" width=\"784\" height=\"560\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}